
{help pss_iteropts:English Version}
{hline}
{* *! version 1.0.1  28may2013}{...}
{synopt: {opt iter:ate(#)}}最大迭代次数；默认值为 
{cmd:iterate(500)}{p_end}
{synopt: {opt tol:erance(#)}}参数容忍度；默认值为 
{cmd:tolerance(1e-12)}{p_end}
{synopt: {opt ftol:erance(#)}}函数容忍度；默认值为 
{cmd:ftolerance(1e-12)}{p_end}
{synopt: [{cmd:no}]{opt log}}禁止或显示迭代日志{p_end}
{synopt: [{cmd:no}]{opt dots}}禁止或显示迭代为点{p_end}